Detailed Description

cvmx_zip_ctl_bist_status

This register has the BIST status of memories in ZIP CTL (instruction buffer, G/S pointer FIFO, input data buffer, output data buffers). Each bit is the BIST result of an individual memory (per bit, 0 = pass and 1 = fail).
